OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBody Shop to shut 75 stores
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fand cut hundreds of jobs   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Body Shop will close 75 shops in   
OL,6, the UK over the coming weeks and cut   
OL,7, 489 jobs, according to the firm        
OL,8, overseeing its restructuring.          
OL,10,FIt means that, combined with           
OL,11,Fcost-cutting at the company's head     
OL,12,Foffice, between 750 and 800 people will
OL,13,Fbe made redundant.                     
OL,15,FHowever, the Body Shop will keep 116 UK
OL,16,Fstores open.                           
OL,18,FThe UK arm of the global beauty chain  
OL,19,Fwas put into administration earlier    
OL,20,Fthis month.                            
